'''Afrika''' i [[tiko-nkulu]] ra vumbirhi hi vukulu naswona i ro sungula hi ntalo wa va aki, after Asia. Ku fikela kwalomu ka 30.2 wa timiliyoni ta km² (11.7 million [[square mile|sq&nbsp;mi]]) kuhlanganisa na swihlala leswi rhendzeleke, ri funengeta kwalomu ka 6% wa [[Misava|misava]] na 20.4% wa vundhzawu hinkwabyo bya misava.<ref name=Sayre>Sayre, April Pulley. (1999) ''Africa'', Twenty-First Century Books. ISBN 0-7613-1367-2.</ref> Kwalomu ka 922 wa timiliyoni ta vanhu (kusukela hi lembe ra 2005)<ref>[http://esa.un.org/unpp/ "World Population Prospects: The 2006 Revision"] [[United Nations]] (Department of Economic and Social Affairs, population division)</ref> e tindhzawini ta 61, ri yimila kwalomu ka  14.2% wa nthsungu wa misava. Tiko-nkulu leri ri rhendzeriwe hi [[Mediterranean Sea|Lwandle ra Meditera]] e nwalungwini, [[Suez Canal]] na [[Red Sea|lwandle ro tshuka]] enwalungwini bya vuxa, lwandle ra Indiya u dzongeni ra vuxa, na lwandle ra Atlantiki e vupela-dyambu. Kuni 53 wa matiko, kuhlanganisa na [[Madagascar]] na swihlala leswi tsongo.

